blackbox: A window manager for X11 written in C++.
blackbox:
blackbox: Blackbox is yet another addition to the list of window managers
blackbox: for X. It is written in C++, sharing no common code with any
blackbox: other window manager (even though the graphics implementation is
blackbox: similar to that of WindowMaker). It features small code size, a
blackbox: fast interface with simple menus, multiple workspaces, decorated
blackbox: windows, built-in graphics code to render solids, gradients,
blackbox: and bevels on the fly, and more.
